    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior, has been meticulously preserved. The engine is in peak performance, and all mechanical components are in perfect working order, offering a driving experience that is essentially like new. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly exceptional, showroom-quality condition.",
