    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who values both performance and long-term reliability. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, it offers an exemplary balance of refined aesthetics and robust mechanical integrity. This offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that has been thoroughly vetted to meet our exacting dealership standards.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is stylish? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently taken care of, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today. It runs like a dream and is perfect for your daily commutes or those fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The chassis remains taut with a reinforced subframe and upgraded bushings to mitigate rear floor fatigue. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, ensuring internal tolerances remain within factory specification. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-driven car, the mechanical integrity is robust, providing the tactile feedback and telepathic handling characteristic of this iconic chassis.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Mechanically sound. Title in hand. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a careful eye will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the lower rear bumper, consistent with standard road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather seats show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, with all electronic features, dual-zone climate control, and the navigation system functioning perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and quiet, backed by a complete service history that confirms regular oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The tires are at roughly 70% tread life, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. While there is a slight bit of curb rash on the passenger-side alloy wheels, the car drives straight and true with no mechanical rattles or concerns. This is a solid, honest car that is ready to be driven home today.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, a testament to rigorous upkeep and professional care. This specimen exhibits strong mechanical performance and a refined interior that remains remarkably composed. Having passed our comprehensive quality assessment, it offers a superior driving experience and aesthetic presence that surpasses standard market offerings. This is a premier choice for the sophisticated driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle without the premium of a new-showroom price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable set of wheels that won't let you down? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready to hit the road with a new owner. It drives super smoothly and is honestly such a joy to be in. Perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, delivering 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. Paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox, it offers a pure mechanical connection and precise gear synchronization. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its weight-saving aluminum subframes and a variable M-differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Critical preventative maintenance\u2014specifically the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014has been addressed to ensure the longevity of the high-revving valvetrain. Finished with a factory carbon fiber roof to lower the center of gravity, this example shows honest signs of use consistent with its age but remains a formidable, high-performance precision tool.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
